ğŸ. ğ’ğ­ğšğ«ğ­ğ®ğ© ğğ«ğ¨ğ›ğ
A startup probe verifies whether the ğšğ©ğ©ğ¥ğ¢ğœğšğ­ğ¢ğ¨ğ§ within the container is started. Startup probes runs ğ›ğğŸğ¨ğ«ğ any other probe and ğğ¢ğ¬ğšğ›ğ¥ğğ¬ any other probes till this probe is completed successfully.
This type of probe is only executed at startup, unlike readiness probes, which are run periodically.
```
