 httpGet:
 path: /healthz
 port: 8080
 initialDelaySeconds: 15
 periodSeconds: 20
```

ğŸ‘. ğ‘ğğšğğ¢ğ§ğğ¬ğ¬ ğğ«ğ¨ğ›ğ
